<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - Housing Society</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #0066cc;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 5px 0 0;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #004d99;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        main h2 {
            color: #0066cc;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #0066cc;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        main p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #004d99;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #80c1ff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            nav a {
                font-size: 0.9em;
                margin: 0 10px;
            }

            main {
                padding: 15px;
            }

            main h2 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Welcome to our Housing Society Privacy Policy page</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#introduction">Introduction</a>
        <a href="#collection">Data Collection</a>
        <a href="#usage">Data Usage</a>
        <a href="#rights">Your Rights</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact Us</a>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section id="introduction">
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="collection">
            <h2>Data Collection</h2>
            <p>We may collect the following information:
                <ul>
                    <li>Personal details (e.g., name, contact information)</li>
                    <li>Housing-related information (e.g., apartment number, parking details)</li>
                    <li>Payment records and transaction history</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="usage">
            <h2>Data Usage</h2>
            <p>Your data is used to provide better services, maintain records, and communicate important updates regarding the society. We do not share your information with third parties without your consent.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="rights">
            <h2>Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal data. To exercise these rights, please contact us directly.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="contact">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, feel free to reach out:
                <ul>
                    <li>Email: support@housingsociety.com</li>
                    <li>Phone: +1 (234) 567-890</li>
                    <li>Office Address: 123 Society Lane, Your City, Your Country</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Housing Society. All rights reserved. | <a href="#">Terms & Conditions</a></p>
